node.title: Man dies in water-related incident at Piha
node.description: A man has died after getting into trouble at Piha beach west of Auckland this morning.
node.content:
["A man has died after getting into trouble at Piha beach west of Auckland this morning.", "", "
File pic Photo: Wikicommons
", "Emergency services were alerted that a person was in difficulty in the water off Marine Parade South at 8.15am.", "Police confirmed he died at the scene.", "A spokesperson said in a statement that police would be making inquiries on behalf of the coroner."]
